metadata.title: Pakistani ambassador, Egypt minister discuss air connectivity

content.article_body:
ISLAMABAD, Oct 20 (APP):Pakistan's ambassador to Egypt Aamir Shouket Monday met with Egypt's Minister of Civil Aviation Dr. Sameh El-Henfy.

According to a post on X, they discussed matters pertaining to enhanced air connectivity and prospects of reviving direct flights between Pakistan and Egypt as a step towards greater people to people and business linkages.
